-----ReadMe-----
SigmaPrint installs under Python3 by default, to switch to Python2, install as normal then apply the Switch to Python2 patch as below


-----Install Full SigmaPrint System--------
1- Add ssh file to boot drive
2- Enable camera, expand rootfs and change password via raspi-config
3- Reboot
4- wget https://github.com/matb97/SigmaPrint/raw/master/build.sh && sudo chmod +x build.sh && ./build.sh

-----Switch to Python2-------
wget https://github.com/matb97/SigmaPrint/raw/master/patches/python3to2.sh && sudo chmod +x python3to2.sh && ./python3to2.sh
